import {Component, EventEmitter, Output, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FormGroup, FormBuilder } from '@angular/forms'; import { FilterService } from './filters-service.model'; @Component({ selector: 'app-filters', templateUrl: './filters.component.html', styleUrls: ['./filters.component.css'] }) export class FiltersComponent implements OnInit{ hideFilters() { const filtersWindow = document.getElementById("filters-window"); // @ts-ignore filtersWindow.style.display = "none"; } myForm!: FormGroup; regions: string[] = []; departements: string[] = []; // Initialisation de la propriété departements communes: string[] = []; constructor(private fb: FormBuilder, private filterService: FilterService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.myForm = this.fb.group({ region: [''], departement: [''], commune: [''] }); this.filterService.getAllRegions().subscribe(regions => this.regions = regions); this.filterService.getAllDepartements().subscribe(departements => this.departements = departements); this.filterService.getAllCommunes().subscribe(communes => this.communes = communes); } }
